  "texts": [
    "19(4), 42500 (2024) 3) Corresponding to the physical function of DBM is the Extended Hydrodynamic Equations (EHE), which include not only the conservation moment evolution equations corresponding to the three conservation laws of mass, momentum, and energy, but also some of the most closely related non-conservation moment evolution equations.",
    "For convenience of description, we refer to the modeling method of deriving EHE based on kinetic equations as Kinetic Macro Modeling (KMM).",
    "Aiguo Xu, et al., Front.",
